main_table.csv:
==============================
name: Galaxy name used in PROBES compendium
RA: Right Ascension coordinate
DEC: Declination coordinate
morphology: Galaxy morphology as given by NED. a '-' symbol means no morphology information available
redshift_helio: Global recessional velocity of galaxy in heliocentric frame
redshift_helio_e: uncertainty on redshift_helio
redshift_cmb: Global recessional velocity of galaxy in cosmic microwave background frame
redshift_cmb_e: uncertainty on redshift_cmb
distance: Distance to galaxy
distance_e: uncertainty on distance
distance_method: method by which distance was calculated
RC_survey: Rotation curve survey from which RC data was drawn. If RC is merged from multiple surveys then they will be listed with a '/' separator
ext_f: Galactic extinction for GALEX FUV-band
ext_n: Galactic extinction for GALEX NUV-band
ext_g: Galactic extinction for DESI g-band
ext_r: Galactic extinction for DESI r-band
ext_z: Galactic extinction for DESI z-band
has_f-band: Boolean for if GALEX FUV-band photometry is avaialable for this galaxy
has_n-band: Boolean for if GALEX NUV-band photometry is avaialable for this galaxy
has_g-band: Boolean for if DESI g-band photometry is avaialable for this galaxy
has_r-band: Boolean for if DESI r-band photometry is avaialable for this galaxy
has_z-band: Boolean for if DESI z-band photometry is avaialable for this galaxy
has_w1-band: Boolean for if unWISE W1-band photometry is avaialable for this galaxy
has_w2-band: Boolean for if unWISE W2-band photometry is avaialable for this galaxy
AutoProf_Flags: Fitting flags are reproduced here to help see the quality of photometry for this galaxy


